{"tid":727113,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"試想像街場踢波日本隊係小學生","createTime":"2018-07-02T20:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T05:02:14.000Z","uid":16055,"like":2,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e635eda72fed0645192fe6ce53ad4445520a7f12","tid":727113,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T20:59:11.000Z","msg":"咁樣想像可以解釋到好多野<br />\n你牛高馬大又實力高過小學雞<br />\n一開始一定會隨便踢諗住可以輕鬆獲勝<br />\n點知班小學雞原來係未來國家隊<br />\n又有技術又射得仲要比佢地入你兩球<br />\n你就會開始發現原來腳下技術唔夠人黎<br />\n於是就屈身高屈體能<br />\n小學雞又未發育又行兩步先等於你一步<br />\n比人反屈返轉頭<br />\n叫做追返兩球<br />\n去到後段 小學雞已經無體力<br />\n又比你追返兩球<br />\n只有盡最後努力博一博<br />\n博唔到之剩仲比人打反擊<br />\n咁就輸左"},{"pid":"8e29bdefa650c83387e485da4f20d1ac8419658a","tid":727113,"uid":61840,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T21:36:29.000Z","msg":"你最sick波啦 比利時無技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42dfb1e45c7556fa13d0465550ec179e9bde5c0","tid":727113,"uid":2502,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T21:40:31.000Z","msg":"屈身高體能有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地嘅優勢黎架喎"},{"pid":"02b377e3272212dc37b18f459fcb3cadd547b7d0","tid":727113,"uid":1139,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T21:43:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b6526c1a7fdcc332434ef8277011cf0404756e4","tid":727113,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T21:44:24.000Z","msg":"咁講法勇士贏硬比利時啦"},{"pid":"114a213f2ed24d60dc69eaec0536894d0431e1b8","tid":727113,"uid":29206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T22:05:57.000Z","msg":"夏薩特 迪布尼腳下技術會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d8d5f0fb2027ea1d6961f4af36f4f864306073","tid":727113,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T22